00:31:32.380 --> 00:31:37.940
to make you aware of a critique
that attaches itself

00:31:37.940 --> 00:31:41.340
to part of the course's
research base.

00:31:41.340 --> 00:31:44.420
One of the things that we have
been doing throughout the

00:31:44.420 --> 00:31:47.420
semester, one of the things
that all of you did in

00:31:47.420 --> 00:31:53.300
directed exercise five, was to
take a look at some of the

00:31:53.300 --> 00:32:01.640
